37
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,680
Yes.

38
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,030
Mr. Qin.

39
00:02:49,870 --> 00:02:50,750
Come in.

40
00:02:56,870 --> 00:02:57,710
Mr. Qin.

41
00:02:57,910 --> 00:02:58,800
