69
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,920
From now on,

70
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,830
I'm at your orders.

71
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:45,310
I wouldn't hesitate

72
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,630
