108
00:08:34,910 --> 00:08:36,960
to have brought the Biyou fruit

109
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,510
from the You Kingdom in time

110
00:08:39,510 --> 00:08:43,000
to Mr. Qin's place in person.

111
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:48,080
