115
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,240
He'll surely like it.

116
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,670
He'll surely like it.

117
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:04,960
My lady.

118
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:08,670
Have you sensed anything?

119
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:13,390
