126
00:09:40,790 --> 00:09:41,790
Mr. Qin.

127
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:46,390
I haven't seen you in days,
but you treat me like a stranger.

128
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,240
Aren't you gonna

129
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,600
