has been reduced,

214
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:03,080
you have me.

215
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:05,550
I can guarantee you a rich life.

216
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:07,270
Mom.

217
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:10,080
