225
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:26,080
and ordered me not to

226
00:14:26,080 --> 00:14:28,030
make trouble with Qin Chen.

227
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:32,910
Mom…

228
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:35,960
