284
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:49,630
Patriarch.

285
00:16:49,630 --> 00:16:51,030
What can we do now?

286
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,030
What do we do?

287
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:58,720
